    <stentry><note type="important">Ensure that all tools are added to your <codeph>PATH</codeph>
            environment variable. To set the variable on Linux and Mac OS X, <xref
              href="http://stackoverflow.com/questions/14637979/how-to-permanently-set-path-on-linux"
              format="html" scope="external">see this page</xref>. To set it on Windows, <xref
              href="http://stackoverflow.com/questions/1618280/where-can-i-set-path-to-make-exe-on-windows"
              format="html" scope="external">see this page</xref>.</note><b>Downloading <keyword
              keyref="prodLong"/></b><p>You can use <keyword keyref="prodShort"/> to push Docker
            images and application code to the server, to start and stop applications, to link
              <keyword keyref="opnStckShort"/> services to applications, and to perform other
            application management operations. <keyword keyref="prodShort"/> works on Linux, Mac OS
            X, and Windows.</p><ul id="ul_cfn_rm1_tt">
            <li><xref
                href="https://helion.hpwsportal.com/catalog.html#/Category/%7B%22categoryId%22%3A10604%7D/Show"
                format="html" scope="external">Download <keyword keyref="prodShort"/>
                <keyword keyref="prodVerLong"/></xref>
            </li>
          </ul><note type="tip">To decompress <codeph>tar.gz</codeph> files on Windows, you can use
            a file archiver such as <xref href="http://www.7-zip.org/" format="html"
              scope="external">7zip</xref>.</note><b>Downloading and Installing the Terraform
            CLI</b><p>The Terraform CLI allows you to construct, manage, update, or delete <keyword
              keyref="prodShort"/> clusters. Click the download link appropriate for your operating
            system:</p><ul id="ul_d1k_5k1_tt">
            <li>Linux <xref
                href="https://releases.hashicorp.com/terraform/0.6.8/terraform_0.6.8_linux_386.zip"
                format="zip" scope="external">x86</xref> | <xref
                href="https://releases.hashicorp.com/terraform/0.6.8/terraform_0.6.8_linux_amd64.zip"
                format="zip" scope="external">x64</xref></li>
            <li>Mac OS X <xref
                href="https://releases.hashicorp.com/terraform/0.6.8/terraform_0.6.8_darwin_386.zip"
                format="zip" scope="external">x86</xref> | <xref
                href="https://releases.hashicorp.com/terraform/0.6.8/terraform_0.6.8_darwin_amd64.zip"
                format="zip" scope="external">x64</xref></li>
            <li>Windows <xref
                href="https://releases.hashicorp.com/terraform/0.6.8/terraform_0.6.8_windows_386.zip"
                format="zip" scope="external">x86</xref> | <xref
                href="https://releases.hashicorp.com/terraform/0.6.8/terraform_0.6.8_windows_amd64.zip"
                format="zip" scope="external">x64</xref></li>
          </ul><b>Downloading and Installing the Cloud Foundry CLI</b><p>The Cloud Foundry CLI
